These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: milk, mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk
Pet: goldfish, rat, fish, cat
1. Pet:cat is on the left of Beverage:iced-tea##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left of Pet:rat##1
3. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:fish is on the left or right of Pet:cat##3
5. Beverage:milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Pet        | goldfish | rat   | cat | fish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: family, horror, spy, time-travel
Nationality: spanish, pakistani, australian, mexican
1. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. Nationality:spanish is on the left of Nationality:australian##1
3. Nationality:australian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:family##1
5. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Nationality:australian##1
6. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:family##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | family  | horror  | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | spanish | australian | pakistani    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: broccoli, cabbage, corn, mango
Movie-Genre: drama, adventure, action, crime
1. Food:mango is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:crime##3
2. Food:corn is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:crime is on the left or right of Food:cabbage##3
4. Movie-Genre:crime is on the right of Movie-Genre:action##1
5. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
6. Food:cabbage is on the right of Food:corn##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | mango | corn | cabbage    | broccoli      |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | crime     | drama | adventure |

