.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: fishing, card-games, camping, singing
Music-Genre: soul, pop, rock, jazz
1. Hobby:card-games is between Music-Genre:soul and Music-Genre:jazz##2
2. Hobby:singing is on the left of Hobby:fishing##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:pop is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Music-Genre:pop is on the right of Hobby:fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | singing | fishing | card-games | camping |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | soul   | pop    | jazz  |

