.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: reggae, dubstep, rock, metal
Nationality: pakistani, nigerian, brazilian, canadian
1. Music-Genre:rock is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1
2. Nationality:nigerian == Music-Genre:metal##1
3. Nationality:brazilian is on the right of Music-Genre:reggae##1
4. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:rock is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:pakistani is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | reggae    | rock   | metal       |
| Nationality   | pakistani | canadian | brazilian | nigerian |

