2. Beverage:sprite is on the left or right of Beverage:soy-milk##3
3. Beverage:cola is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:broccoli is on the left of Food:mango##1
5. Food:mango is on the right of Beverage:soy-milk##1
6. Food:broccoli is in an even position##4
7. Food:garlic == Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk    | sprite       | mirinda |
| Food       | lemon  | broccoli | mango | garlic  |

